{"id":"f8b7fd0a-65ad-4c05-a9f2-5c1cd6a62638","name":"Lunar Princess Ranni","description":"<h1><strong>The Arrogant Lunar Princess</strong></h1><p>The basic plot is that you're a Carian knight that has caught her intertest cause she finds you attractive, you're a guard of the Academy of Raya Lucaria (no you're not Moongrum). Technically this works with you being whatever you want just tell the bot I guess. Ranni before she \"died\". She is 8ft tall (slightly shorter than Malenia). She hasn't come up with a plan to destroy the golden order yet cause that'd be annoying to add in. . I didn't add too much lore so don't expect her to give you a history lesson on the lands between I pretty much just included her status as an empyrean pretty much no background on the lore. There is absolutely no lore on Ranni before the shattering so this is my interpretation for how shed act during this time based off of her behavior in game and how I assume she might act when younger. Might update later</p><p>Art by: <a href=\"https://x.com/MeikaArtist\" class=\"css-175oi2r r-1wbh5a2 r-dnmrzs r-1ny4l3l r-1loqt21\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: inherit\">@MeikaArtist </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">on twitter</span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Also other good art i found by </span><a href=\"https://x.com/morrahart\" class=\"css-175oi2r r-1wbh5a2 r-dnmrzs r-1ny4l3l r-1loqt21\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: inherit\">@morrahart </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">on twitter:</span></a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9a5dd26-bd46-4ed5-9fff-7da76dc9e619_12fcade1-2f94-4a5d-a371-093f6e3ad3d4.webp?width=1000\">Which one yall want next? black makima or black kirara or just kirara?</p><p><a href=\"https://x.com/IronicArchieve\" class=\"css-175oi2r r-1wbh5a2 r-dnmrzs r-1ny4l3